      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "KING GANDO (1) has missed the frame at his last couple of starts but just a few runs back broke the clock when winning over 461m at this track, taking a Grade 6 in an excellent 25.83. Expected to push the clock again here. SCARRED (2) has been a little hard to follow, finishing out of the placings latest but was in winning form two back scoring in a Grade 6 at this track. Expecting sharp improvement this line-up. LIZZY'S GIRL (7) turned in a good run last time, finishing in the placings (29.79) at Launceston in a Special conditions race. Lines up from box 7 for the first time. Can feature again. ROJO SAILIE (3) must be respected despite an unplaced effort here most recently.",
